flc.nbl_actors.experimental.log

Class MsgListenerFactoryRingBuf

  • java.lang.Object
    • flc.nbl_actors.experimental.log.MessageEventBuffer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMsgListenerFactory, IMsgTrace, java.util.function.Consumer<IMsgEvent>

    public class MsgListenerFactoryRingBuf
extends java.lang.Object
implements IMsgListenerFactory, java.util.function.Consumer<IMsgEvent>, IMsgTrace
    Default message event logger, where events are added to a single synchronized ring-buffer. Multiple calls to forkListener() returns the same logger instance.

    Date 16.01.2015.
